title: Four sisters drown in Balochistanâ€™s Duki - Pakistan - DAWN.COM
content:
QUETTA: Four sisters drowned while taking bath in a seasonal stream in Duki area of Balochistan on Friday.

Officials said the incident took place in Anmbar seasonal stream in UC Lakhi-2. They said that Suwa Bibi, 5, and her two sisters went deep into the stream water while bathing.

Published in Dawn, July 26th, 2025
